WEBVTT

00:38.780 --> 00:42.850
<b>蒂姆·罗宾斯</b>

00:44.750 --> 00:48.820
<b>摩根·弗里曼</b>

00:51.090 --> 00:55.460
<b>肖申克的救赎</b>

00:55.960 --> 00:57.460
<b></b>

02:05.610 --> 02:07.270
<b>杜弗瑞恩先生</b><b>
Mr. Dufresne, describe...</b>

02:07.770 --> 02:12.110
<b>请描述一下你妻子遇害当晚你们吵架时的情况</b><b>
the confrontation you had with your wife the night she was murdered.</b>

02:16.780 --> 02:18.290
<b>我非常痛苦</b><b>
It was very bitter.</b>

02:18.790 --> 02:23.120
<b>她说被我发现反倒轻松多了 再也不用成天提心吊胆的了</b><b>
She said she was glad I knew, that she hated all the sneaking around.</b>

02:24.660 --> 02:27.900
<b>美国著名的"离婚城市" 凡欲离婚者 在该市住满三个月即可获准离婚</b>

02:24.660 --> 02:27.900
<b>她还说她要去里诺市和我离婚</b><b>
And she said that she wanted a divorce in Reno.</b>

02:28.400 --> 02:31.770
<b>- 你当时是如何回答她的? - 我告诉她我不会同意</b><b>
- What was your response? - I told her I would not grant one.</b>

02:32.270 --> 02:35.140
<b>"我怕你活不到在里诺市见我的那天了!"</b><b>
"I'll see you in hell before I see you in Reno."</b>

02:35.640 --> 02:38.970
<b>据你邻居的证词 杜弗瑞恩先生 这是你当时的回答</b><b>
Those were your words, according to your neighbors.</b>

02:40.040 --> 02:41.670
<b>也许吧</b><b>
If they say so.</b>

02:42.180 --> 02:44.480
<b>我的确不记得了 当时完全气昏头了</b><b>
I really don't remember. I was upset.</b>

02:44.980 --> 02:47.410
<b>你们吵完架之后发生了什么事?</b><b>
What happened after you argued with your wife?</b>

02:48.580 --> 02:50.350
<b>她收拾了一包东西</b><b>
She packed a bag.</b>

02:51.520 --> 02:54.680
<b>她收了包东西 搬到昆汀先生那儿去住了</b><b>
She packed a bag to go and stay with Mr. Quentin.</b>

02:55.320 --> 02:59.130
<b>格伦·昆汀 斯诺登俱乐部高尔夫教练</b><b>
Glenn Quentin, golf pro at the Snowden Hills Country Club...</b>

02:59.630 --> 03:02.750
<b>其被你发现与你妻子偷情</b><b>
whom you had discovered was your wife's lover.</b>

03:05.070 --> 03:06.260
<b>你有没有尾随她?</b><b>
Did you follow her?</b>

03:07.600 --> 03:09.400
<b>我先是去的酒吧</b><b>
I went to a few bars first.</b>

03:09.900 --> 03:14.270
<b>之后 我开车去昆汀家找他们 但他们不在</b><b>
Later, I drove to his house to confront them. They weren't home.</b>

03:14.840 --> 03:16.370
<b>我把车停在路岔口</b><b>
I parked in the turnout...</b>

03:17.080 --> 03:17.780
<b>在车里等</b><b>
and waited.</b>

03:18.280 --> 03:19.940
<b>当时你有什么企图?</b><b>
With what intention?</b>

03:20.550 --> 03:21.980
<b>我自己到现在也说不清</b><b>
I'm not sure.</b>

03:23.120 --> 03:24.290
<b>当时我心里很乱</b><b>
I was confused...</b>

03:24.790 --> 03:25.840
<b>又喝了不少酒</b><b>
drunk.</b>

03:27.350 --> 03:28.360
<b>我想</b><b>
I think...</b>

03:28.860 --> 03:30.690
<b>顶多也就是想吓吓他们而已</b><b>
mostly I wanted to scare them.</b>

03:31.190 --> 03:34.590
<b>他们回来后 你就进屋杀了他们</b><b>
When they arrived, you went up to the house and murdered them.</b>

03:35.530 --> 03:36.600
<b>没有 我开始清醒过来</b><b>
No.I was sobering up.</b>

03:37.100 --> 03:40.470
<b>回到车子里 然后开车回家 想着睡一觉会好过一些</b><b>
I got back in the car and I drove home to sleep it off.</b>

03:40.970 --> 03:43.640
<b>半路上 我停车把枪扔进了Royal河里</b><b>
Along the way, I threw my gun into the Royal River.</b>

03:44.140 --> 03:45.870
<b>这一点我记得很清楚</b><b>
I've been very clear on this point.</b>

03:46.370 --> 03:50.140
<b>离奇的是次日一早清洁女佣发现</b><b>
I get hazy where the cleaning woman shows up the following morning...</b>

03:50.640 --> 03:52.950
<b>你妻子和她的情人在床上</b><b>
and finds your wife in bed with her lover...</b>

03:53.450 --> 03:55.540
<b>被点三八口径的子弹打得如同马蜂窝一般</b><b>
riddled with.38-caliber bullets.</b>

03:56.920 --> 04:01.120
<b>你不觉得这种巧合来得太蹊跷了吗? 还是只有我这么认为</b><b>
Does that strike you as a fantastic coincidence, or is it just me?</b>

04:02.020 --> 04:02.720
<b>的确很蹊跷</b><b>
Yes, it does.</b>

04:03.220 --> 04:05.520
<b>然而你仍旧坚持在凶案发生前</b><b>
Yet you still maintain you threw your gun into the river...</b>

04:06.020 --> 04:08.360
<b>你已经把枪扔进河里</b><b>
before the murders took place.</b>

04:08.860 --> 04:10.800
<b>这个说法倒是很省事</b><b>
That's very convenient.</b>

04:11.300 --> 04:12.830
<b>这是事实</b><b>
It's the truth.</b>

04:13.330 --> 04:17.600
<b>警方花三天时间摸遍了整条河道 并没找到一把枪</b><b>
The police dragged that river for three days, and nary a gun was found...</b>

04:18.100 --> 04:21.910
<b>因此也就无法鉴定命中受害者的那些子弹</b><b>
so no comparison could be made between your gun and the bullets...</b>

04:22.410 --> 04:25.850
<b>是否与你那把枪的弹道相吻合</b><b>
taken from the bloodstained corpses of the victims.</b>

04:26.510 --> 04:28.880
<b>这对你来说同样非常省事</b><b>
And that also...</b>

04:29.380 --> 04:32.820
<b>不是吗 杜弗瑞恩先生?</b><b>
is very convenient. Isn't it, Mr. Dufresne?</b>

04:34.150 --> 04:35.920
<b>恰恰因为我是无辜的 先生</b><b>
Since I am innocent of this crime...</b>

04:36.420 --> 04:41.050
<b>所以找不到枪反倒对我非常麻烦</b><b>
I find it decidedly inconvenient that the gun was never found.</b>

04:58.950 --> 05:02.020
<b>诸位陪审员 你们听到了所有的证据</b><b>
Ladies and gentlemen, you've heard all the evidence.</b>

05:02.520 --> 05:06.050
<b>被告曾到过凶案现场 并留下脚印</b><b>
We have the accused at the scene of the crime. We have footprints.</b>

05:06.550 --> 05:09.120
<b>散落在现场的子弹上有被告的指纹</b><b>
Bullets on the ground bearing his fingerprints.</b>

05:09.620 --> 05:12.290
<b>还有一只打碎的酒瓶 同样有他的指纹</b><b>
A broken bourbon bottle, likewise with fingerprints.</b>

05:12.790 --> 05:14.060
<b>最重要的是</b><b>
And most of all...</b>

05:14.560 --> 05:17.330
<b>一位漂亮的年轻妇人和她的情人</b><b>
we have a beautiful young woman and her lover...</b>

05:17.830 --> 05:19.860
<b>双双死在对方的怀抱中</b><b>
lying dead in each other's arms.</b>

05:21.030 --> 05:23.660
<b>他们是有过错</b><b>
They had sinned.</b>

05:24.870 --> 05:27.170
<b>但他们的过错是否严重到</b><b>
But was their crime so great...</b>

05:27.670 --> 05:29.580
<b>需要付出生命作为代价呢?</b><b>
as to merit a death sentence?</b>

05:30.080 --> 05:32.370
<b>在你们作出结论之前</b><b>
While you think about that...</b>

05:33.810 --> 05:35.610
<b>请先看看这个</b><b>
think about this:</b>

05:36.480 --> 05:39.920
<b>一只左轮手枪只能填装六颗子弹 而不是八颗</b><b>
A revolver holds six bullets, not eight.</b>

05:40.420 --> 05:43.820
<b>所以我认定这不是一时冲动才犯下的罪行</b><b>
I submit that this was not a hot-blooded crime of passion.</b>

05:44.320 --> 05:46.830
<b>即使那不能被宽恕 至少还可以理解</b><b>
That at least could be understood, if not condoned.</b>

05:47.330 --> 05:48.060
<b>不是!</b><b>
No.</b>

05:48.560 --> 05:49.400
<b>这是一次复仇行为</b><b>
This was revenge...</b>

05:49.900 --> 05:53.480
<b>出于一种特别残忍 冷血的本性</b><b>
of a much more brutal, cold-blooded nature. Consider this:</b>

05:53.980 --> 05:56.930
<b>想想看 每个受害人身中四枪</b><b>
Four bullets per victim.</b>

05:57.670 --> 05:59.400
<b>总共开了八枪 而不是六枪</b><b>
Not six shots fired, but eight.</b>

05:59.910 --> 06:03.240
<b>那表明他打完一轮子弹后</b><b>
That means that he fired the gun empty...</b>

06:03.740 --> 06:05.410
<b>曾停下来填装子弹</b><b>
and then stopped to reload...</b>

06:05.910 --> 06:09.080
<b>然后继续向受害人开枪</b><b>
so that he could shoot each of them again.</b>

06:09.580 --> 06:11.530
<b>每人补射一枪</b><b>
An extra bullet per lover...</b>

06:12.030 --> 06:14.680
<b>正中头部!</b><b>
right in the head.</b>

06:18.190 --> 06:22.900
<b>杜弗瑞恩先生 你的冷酷无情 不知悔改让人震惊</b><b>
You strike me as a particularly icy and remorseless man, Mr. Dufresne.</b>

06:23.400 --> 06:25.520
<b>看到你都令我心寒齿冷</b><b>
It chills my blood just to look at you.</b>

06:27.470 --> 06:29.940
<b>依据缅因州赋予我的权利</b><b>
By the power vested in me by the state of Maine...</b>

06:30.440 --> 06:34.580
<b>我判处你连服两项终身监禁</b><b>
I hereby order you to serve two life sentences back-to-back...</b>

06:35.080 --> 06:37.600
<b>分别告慰两位受害人 退庭!</b><b>
one for each of your victims. So be it!</b>

07:02.740 --> 07:03.900
<b>坐!</b><b>
Sit.</b>

07:08.440 --> 07:11.270
<b>你因被判终身监禁己在此服刑二十年?</b><b>
We see you've served 20 years of a life sentence?</b>

07:12.210 --> 07:15.320
<b>- 是的 先生 - 你认为你已经改过自新了吗?</b><b>
- Yes, sir. - You feel you've been rehabilitated?</b>

07:15.820 --> 07:18.410
<b>是的 先生 绝对改了 先生</b><b>
Yes, sir. Absolutely, sir.</b>

07:19.550 --> 07:21.540
<b>我是说 我已经接受教训了</b><b>
I mean, I learned my lesson.</b>

07:22.620 --> 07:26.060
<b>说实话我已经完全改变了</b><b>
I can honestly say that I'm a changed man.</b>

07:29.300 --> 07:31.370
<b>我不再对社会有威胁了</b><b>
I'm no longer a danger to society.</b>

07:31.870 --> 07:33.830
<b>我可以向上帝保证</b><b>
That's God's honest truth.</b>

07:39.540 --> 07:40.130
<b>驳回</b>

08:10.140 --> 08:11.140
<b>嗨 瑞德</b><b>
Hey, Red.</b>

08:11.640 --> 08:12.640
<b>怎么样啊?</b><b>
How'd it go?</b>

08:13.140 --> 08:15.080
<b>还能怎么样? 日子不同罢了</b><b>
Same old shit, different day.</b>

08:15.580 --> 08:17.140
<b>我知道你心里什么滋味</b><b>
Yeah, I know how you feel.</b>

08:17.640 --> 08:19.640
<b>下周轮到我要去申请"驳回"了</b><b>
I'm up for rejection next week.</b>

08:20.410 --> 08:22.650
<b>是啊 我是上周被"驳回"的</b><b>
Yeah, I got rejected last week.</b>

08:23.150 --> 08:24.150
<b>一向如此</b><b>
It happens.</b>

08:24.650 --> 08:25.790
<b>嗨 瑞德 借我一包烟</b><b>
Hey, Red, bump me a deck.</b>

08:26.290 --> 08:29.320
<b>离我远点伙计! 你都欠我五包烟了</b><b>
Get out of my face, man! You're into me for five packs already.</b>

08:29.820 --> 08:30.790
<b>- 四包! - 五包!</b><b>
Four!</b>

08:31.930 --> 08:35.060
<b>美国的每座监狱里大概都有像我一样的人物</b><b>
There must be a con like me in every prison in America.</b>

08:35.560 --> 08:37.060
<b>我就是能够给你搞进来东西的那个人</b><b>
I'm the guy who can get it for you.</b>

08:37.560 --> 08:40.370
<b>香烟 大麻 只要你喜欢</b><b>
Cigarettes, a bag of reefer, if that's your thing...</b>

08:40.870 --> 08:44.000
<b>或者孩子高中毕业 你想来瓶白兰地高兴一下</b><b>
bottle of brandy to celebrate your kid's high school graduation.</b>

08:44.500 --> 08:46.340
<b>几乎任何合理的需求</b><b>
Damn near anything within reason.</b>

08:46.840 --> 08:49.500
<b>美国著名连锁公司 以百货零售著称</b>

08:46.840 --> 08:49.500
<b>信不信由你 我差不多就是这里正规经营的 西尔斯&罗巴克 </b><b>
Yes, sir! I'm a regular Sears and Roebuck.</b>

08:53.510 --> 08:56.150
<b>所以当安迪·杜弗瑞恩1949年来找我</b><b>
So when Andy Dufresne came to me in 1949...</b>

08:56.650 --> 08:59.920
<b>1940年代好莱坞著名女星 以性感著称</b>

08:56.650 --> 08:59.920
<b>让我替他搞张 丽塔·海华斯的海报进来时</b><b>
and asked me to smuggle Rita Hayworth into the prison for him...</b>

09:00.420 --> 09:02.680
<b>我跟他说 "没问题"</b><b>
I told him, "No problem."</b>

09:44.560 --> 09:46.470
<b>安迪是1947年开春时节被送到肖申克监狱的</b><b>
Andy came to Shawshank Prison...</b>

09:46.970 --> 09:50.670
<b>罪名是谋杀他的妻子和她的小白脸</b><b>
in early 1947 for murdering his wife and the fella she was banging.</b>

09:51.170 --> 09:55.180
<b>入狱以前 他是波特兰银行的副总裁</b><b>
On the outside, he'd been vice president of a large Portland bank.</b>

09:55.680 --> 09:57.470
<b>年青有为</b><b>
Good work for a man so young.</b>

10:40.720 --> 10:42.190
<b>你会说英语吗 肥牛?</b><b>
You speak English, butt-steak?</b>

10:42.690 --> 10:44.550
<b>跟这个长官走</b><b>
You follow this officer.</b>

10:57.300 --> 11:01.310
<b>我这辈子还没见过一堆长这么烂的杂碎</b><b>
I never seen such a sorry-Iooking heap of maggot shit in all my life.</b>

11:01.810 --> 11:04.400
<b>嗨菜鸟! 到这儿来!</b><b>
Hey, fish! Come over here!</b>

11:27.670 --> 11:28.940
<b>今天要赌吗 瑞德?</b><b>
Taking bets today, Red?</b>

11:29.440 --> 11:30.840
<b>赌烟还是赌钱? 自己选</b><b>
Smokes or coin? Bettor's choice.</b>

11:31.340 --> 11:33.030
<b>香烟 我赌两根</b><b>
Smokes. Put me down for two.</b>

11:33.570 --> 11:34.840
<b>好吧 你押哪匹马?</b><b>
All right, who's your horse?</b>

11:35.340 --> 11:37.060
<b>又矮又瘦那个</b><b>
That little sack of shit.</b>

11:37.560 --> 11:44.080
<b>- 第八个 排第八那个 我赌他最快 - 不可能! 我和你赌! 你输定了</b><b>
- Eighth. He'll be first. - Bullshit! I'll take that action.</b>

11:44.580 --> 11:46.090
<b>海伍德 就你机灵 那你押啊</b><b>
If you're so smart, you call it.</b>

11:46.590 --> 11:49.360
<b>我押那个大屁股</b><b>
I'll take that chubby fat-ass there.</b>

11:49.860 --> 11:52.450
<b>排在第五的那个 五根香烟</b><b>
The fifth one. Put me down for a quarter deck.</b>

11:55.660 --> 11:57.360
<b>菜鸟上市啦!</b><b>
Fresh fish today!</b>

11:58.130 --> 11:59.600
<b>又有操练的啦!</b><b>
We're reeling them in!</b>

12:00.270 --> 12:03.930
<b>我得承认第一眼看到安迪的时候并没觉得他有什么特别</b><b>
I admit I didn't think much of Andy first time I laid eyes on him.</b>

12:04.470 --> 12:07.210
<b>他看上去弱不胜衣 仿佛一阵风就能吹跑</b><b>
Looked like a stiff breeze would blow him over.</b>

12:07.710 --> 12:09.540
<b>这是我对他的第一印象</b><b>
That was my first impression of the man.</b>

12:10.040 --> 12:11.180
<b>你押哪个?</b><b>
What do you say?</b>

12:11.680 --> 12:14.680
<b>那个大个子 一身富贵子弟打扮那个</b><b>
That tall drink of water with the silver spoon up his ass.</b>

12:15.180 --> 12:17.020
<b>那家伙? 不可能!</b><b>
That guy? Never happen.</b>

12:17.520 --> 12:19.490
<b>- 我赌十根香烟! - 那可是笔大买卖!</b><b>
- 10 cigarettes. - That's a rich bet.</b>

12:19.990 --> 12:21.760
<b>都有谁想来赢我?</b><b>
Who's going to prove me wrong?</b>

12:22.260 --> 12:23.860
<b>海伍德? 济格?</b><b>
Heywood? Jigger?</b>

12:24.360 --> 12:25.360
<b>斯基兹?</b><b>
Skeets?</b>

12:25.860 --> 12:27.190
<b>弗洛伊德?</b><b>
Floyd!</b>

12:28.130 --> 12:29.900
<b>四个猛男</b><b>
Four brave souls.</b>

12:30.400 --> 12:32.870
<b>马上返回本人牢房 准备点名!</b><b>
Return to your cellblocks for evening count.</b>

12:33.370 --> 12:36.670
<b>所有人犯马上返回自己牢房!</b><b>
All prisoners, return to your cellblocks.</b>

12:57.060 --> 12:57.890
<b>向右转!</b><b>
Turn to the right!</b>

12:58.390 --> 12:59.690
<b>向前看!</b><b>
Eyes front.</b>

13:12.770 --> 13:15.080
<b>这位是哈德利先生 他是看守长</b><b>
This is Mr. Hadley. He's captain of the guards.</b>

13:15.580 --> 13:17.380
<b>我是诺顿先生 典狱长</b><b>
I'm Mr. Norton, the warden.</b>

13:17.880 --> 13:19.880
<b>你们都是被判有罪的恶棍</b><b>
You are convicted felons.</b>

13:20.380 --> 13:22.370
<b>因此被送到我这里来</b><b>
That's why they've sent you to me.</b>

13:22.950 --> 13:24.050
<b>规则一</b><b>
Rule number one:</b>

13:24.550 --> 13:26.040
<b>不得亵渎神明!</b><b>
No blasphemy.</b>

13:26.550 --> 13:29.690
<b>在我的监狱里不准许对主的名字不敬</b><b>
I'll not have the Lord's name taken in vain in my prison.</b>

13:30.190 --> 13:31.090
<b>其它规则</b><b>
The other rules...</b>

13:31.590 --> 13:34.760
