God's honest truth.</b>

1:13:46.440 --> 1:13:48.530
<b>绝对改过自新了</b><b>
Absolutely rehabilitated.</b>

1:13:52.280 --> 1:13:53.340
<b>驳回</b>

1:13:58.510 --> 1:13:59.840
