Jesus, when you say it like that...</b>

1:14:04.580 --> 1:14:06.380
<b>不知道怎么过去的是吧?</b><b>
You wonder where it went.</b>

1:14:08.040 --> 1:14:10.980
<b>我是不知道我这十年是怎么过去的</b><b>
I wonder where 10 years went.</b>

1:14:15.960 --> 1:14:16.930
<b>这个...</b><b>
Here.</b>

1:14:17.430 --> 1:14:20.160
<b>是给你假释被拒的小礼物</b><b>
A little parole rejection present.</b>

1:14:21.430 --> 1:14:23.130
<b>打来看看!</b><b>
Go ahead and open it.</b>

1:14:24.240 --> 1:14:25.970
<b>从你同行那儿买的</b><b>
Went through one of your competitors.</b>

1:14:26.470 --> 1:14:29.600
<b>希望你不会介意 我是想给你个惊喜</b><b>
I hope you don't mind. I wanted it to be a surprise.</b>

1:14:39.650 --> 1:14:41.140
<b>说实话 真的很漂亮</b><b>
It's very pretty, indeed.</b>

1:14:42.860 --> 1:14:44.050
<b>谢谢你</b><b>
Thank you.</b>

1:14:46.630 --> 1:14:48.090
<b>你打算吹吗?</b><b>
You going to play it?</b>

1:14:52.670 --> 1:14:53.930
<b>不</b><b>
No.</b>

1:14:57.540 --> 1:14:58.940
<b>现在不打算</b><b>
Not right now.</b>

1:15:16.620 --> 1:15:17.720
<b>进囚室!</b><b>
Roll in!</b>

1:15:31.030 --> 1:15:34.360
<b>新一代美女 纪念你的十周年 瑞德</b>

1:15:53.930 --> 1:15:55.160
<b>熄灯!</b><b>
Lights out!</b>

